quran[8{c,v,t}:
7,88,"is ki qoum ke sardaro ne, jo apni barayi ke ghamand mein mubtala thay, a seen se kaha ke"" ae Shoiab, hum tujhe aur unn logon ko jo tairay sath imaan laaye hain apni bastii se nikaal den ge warna tum logon ko hamari millat mein wapas aana hoga"" Shoiab ne jawab diya"" kya zabardasti hamein phera jaye ga khuwa hum raazi nah hon ?"
7,89,"hum Allah par jhoot gharnay walay hon ge agar tumhari millat mein palat ayen jabkay Allah hamein is se nijaat day chuka hai hamaray liye to is ki taraf palatna ab kisi terhan mumkin nahi ila yeh ke khuda hamara rab hi aisa chahay hamaray rab ka ilm har cheez par haawi hai, usi par hum ne aetmaad kar liya ae rab, hamaray aur hamari qoum ke darmain theek theek faisla kar day aur to behtareen faisla karne wala hai """
7,90,"is ki qoum ke sardaro ne, jo is ki baat maan-ne se inkaar kar chuke thay, aapas mein kaha"" agar tum ne Shoiab ki pairwi qubool kar li to barbaad ho jao ge """
7,91,magar howa yeh ke aik dhula dainay wali aafat ne unn ko aa liya aur woh apne gharon mein avndhe parre ke parre reh gay
7,92,jin logon ne Shoiab ko jhtlaya woh aisay mite ke goya kabhi un gharon mein basey hi nah thay Shoiab ke jhutlanay walay hi aakhir-kaar barbaad ho kar rahay
7,93,"aur Shoiab yeh keh kar un ki bustiyon se nikal gaya ke"" ae baradran qoum, mein ne apne rab ke paighamaat tumhe pouncha diye aur tumhari kher khawahi ka haq ada kar diya ab mein uss qoum par kaisay afsos karoon jo qubool haq se inkaar karti hai """
7,94,kabhi aisa nahi howa ke hum ne kisi bastii mein nabi bheja ho aur uss bastii ke logon ko pehlay tangi aur sakhti mein mubtala nah kya ho is khayaal se ke shayad woh aajzi par utar ayen
7,95,"phir hum ne un ki badhaali ko khush haali se badal diya yahan taq ke woh khoob phalay phoolay aur kehnay lagey ke"" hamaray islaaf par bhi achay aur buray din atay hi rahay hain"" aakhir-kaar hum ne inhen achanak pakar liya aur inhen khabar taq nah hui"
